### Todo List API - Exemplos de Uso

### 1. Cadastrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3333/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Fazer login
POST http://localhost:3333/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Criar projeto
POST http://localhost:3333/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Projeto Trabalho",
  "description": "Tarefas relacionadas ao trabalho"
}

### 4. Listar projetos
GET http://localhost:3333/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Criar tarefa sem projeto
POST http://localhost:3333/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Comprar pão",
  "description": "Comprar pão na padaria",
  "dueDate": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}

### 6. Criar tarefa com projeto
POST http://localhost:3333/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Implementar API",
  "description": "Criar endpoints da API REST",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "note": "Prioridade alta"
}

### 7. Listar tarefas
GET http://localhost:3333/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Marcar tarefa como concluída
PATCH http://localhost:3333/todos/{{todoId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Criar subtarefa
POST http://localhost:3333/todos/{{todoId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Criar endpoint de autenticação",
  "description": "Implementar login e registro"
}

### 10. Listar subtarefas
GET http://localhost:3333/todos/{{todoId}}/subtasks
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 11. Marcar subtarefa como concluída
PATCH http://localhost:3333/subtasks/{{subtaskId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 12. Listar tarefas de um projeto específico
GET http://localhost:3333/projects/{{projectId}}/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 13. Excluir subtarefa
DELETE http://localhost:3333/subtasks/{{subtaskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 14. Excluir tarefa
DELETE http://localhost:3333/todos/{{todoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 15. Excluir projeto
DELETE http://localhost:3333/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 16. Health check
GET http://localhost:3333/health

### 17. Documentação Swagger
GET http://localhost:3333/docs

### Variáveis para usar no VS Code REST Client:
# @authToken = token_jwt_aqui
# @projectId = id_do_projeto_aqui
# @todoId = id_da_tarefa_aqui
# @subtaskId = id_da_subtarefa_aqui 